{"tid":1833974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉去黃店查商業登記","createTime":"2020-01-22T07:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T07:50:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ab36c4a590a925f62d4f475ab6e0025ae613a8f3","tid":1833974,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"今日中午，馳名中外嘅Regina葉劉姐姐突然嚟到我哋銅鑼灣店😱<br />\n<br />\n咁啱今日腦細罕有地喺廚房扮緊工，佢一嚟到就order左一個外賣，問店員老細喺邊度。之後就直殺左入廚房🤪<br />\n<br />\n一入到黎就就問我哋有冇登記做選民。腦細問：「乜你而家負責做選民登記咩？我哋一早登記左啦。廚房危險喎，有冇乜嘢幫到你」姐姐笑說：「我都係幫個同事手姐，佢哋驚啲黃色經濟...你哋個商業登記喺邊度啊？」<br />\n<br />\n其實商業登記一大個癡咗喺廳面，話咗俾佢知之後佢就出去係咁影📸📸📸<br />\n<br />\n忙完一大輪之後，老細決定親自送佢一程出門口，順便講一句，多謝你支持黃色小店喎💛💛姐姐打個突，話：「冇問題...最緊要唔好暴力啦🤪...同埋最好唔好搞乜嘢黃色經濟啦🤨」之後就急急腳走咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n為咗紀念佢對黃色經濟圈嘅支持，我地決定將佢嘅現金化為愛心，全數捐比立場新聞🥰🥰🥰 Bye <br />\n<br />\n#當堂嚇一跳 #然後得啖笑 #呀條友真係唔識架喎 #驚驚 ￼#記得登記做選民啊 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=773033616540147&amp;id=194958111014370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D773033616540147%26id%3D194958111014370&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d1a66ca4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=773033616540147&amp;id=194958111014370</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMCiUYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMCiUYa.jpg&h=568873f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c149023a0314c7ca362a0007c595f9140f244ed6","tid":1833974,"uid":243125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"中共驚飲食界功能組別比我地翻盤"},{"pid":"8b3063a77ecd199afb869a9ef6c9640d5e119d10","tid":1833974,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:28:20.000Z","msg":"葉劉都支持，藍絲仲唔一齊幫襯"},{"pid":"6b927eb69d5a1cdb3c27aacb93302c2c67cbc7ee","tid":1833974,"uid":43939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"對家驚到咁就知好值得做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f93cd97d7a8c1f784d69e43dce0ef073e25eb2b","tid":1833974,"uid":316420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"黑絲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d01391cb8b5cb8d97365c0e8741f94c8525216","tid":1833974,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"葉劉去宣傳？<br />\n<br />\n今年小心麒麟啊"},{"pid":"63d9cbcae0eca8dde88db62aa80dd25b1ee63663","tid":1833974,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"死亡之吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8477ff1cb09454922c725b11b5e93d77af9becb","tid":1833974,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:41:55.000Z","msg":"親自出馬咁冇人？<br />\n<br />\n亡咗黨？"},{"pid":"c5fced82e6fc92535cd5612053fa04a13e6afd7e","tid":1833974,"uid":271513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"大家要努力組隊，勸喻食店做選民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fe76979caee3bcfe17c2ffa745ad5d158f4bee","tid":1833974,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T07:50:52.000Z","msg":"題外話：<br />\n<br />\n呢間嘢有任食薯片，<br />\n同埋啲男店員幾高大靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}